QuestData.Title: Explorers' League Document (6 of 6)
QuestData.Description: The document bears the Explorers' League crest and contains detailed assessments of the various threats present within Loch Modan. Sooty smudges lead you to believe it was likely stolen by the Dark Iron spies in the area.$B$BYou recall mention of missing documents at the Explorers' League building in Thelsamar.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return the Explorers' League Document to Torren Squarejaw in Thelsamar.
QuestData.RewardText: Hah! Think they got a kick out of seeing how low they were on our list of threat assessments? This document was admittedly a bit out of date, but none the less amusing.$B$BOf course, we'll offer you some money as a reward for returning this anyway - your efforts are appreciated!
